WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:07.824
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us. Well, it's Diana and Brandon. Thank you for joining us.

00:00:07.825 --> 00:00:15.469
Truly, we're so blessed to have you all pray with us every single time we do these videos. We were so excited, Braden.

00:00:15.470 --> 00:00:30.990
We got the report and it said we're number five because of you all coming and praying with us—of the most viewed, most watched Christian channels on YouTube.

00:00:30.991 --> 00:00:38.799
Yeah, I told D, I go, "Are you kidding me? Top five. We're in the top five."Praise God. Oh, glory to God, ladies and gentlemen.

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:47.000
I said, "Lord, look what you've done in just a short amount of time."He said, "Brandon, there's much more to come. There's much more to come, son.

00:00:47.001 --> 00:01:02.893
As you stay vertical, as you stay focused, as you attract to deflect, it's all about Jesus."But in this, I want to celebrate a milestone of being in the top five most watched Christian channels on YouTube.

00:01:02.894 --> 00:01:11.546
Look what God did. Look what God did. It just wows us. He wows us, but you all supporting it so much.

00:01:11.547 --> 00:01:18.719
I think above us was Steven Furtick and T.D. Jakes and another channel I've never heard of before.

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:27.712
It's amazing because we know those people have huge channels with millions of followers.

00:01:27.713 --> 00:01:30.803
And the Lord said, "It isn't about how many are following you, son.

00:01:30.804 --> 00:01:35.399
It's about how many are coming and watching every single day and praying."How many are praying?

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.748
We've got some praying people out there. Not subscribers, prayers.

00:01:38.749 --> 00:01:44.716
Yeah, we're not looking for subscribers; we're looking for many people to enlist in the army of God.

00:01:44.717 --> 00:01:54.676
That's what we're after, and it's just exciting. Most people go, "Well, you're bragging."I know it's not about me. If you knew how incapable I am of doing these videos...

00:01:54.677 --> 00:02:08.001
People say, "Well, you're good behind the camera."I said, "If you knew before, I was scared spitless to come on here and talk in front of that camera."And I told Diana, every single time we did it, we did it over and over again, practicing and just saying, "Lord, use whatever you can.

00:02:08.002 --> 00:02:16.795
If you can use anybody, Lord, you can use me."I mean, seriously, it's amazing what the Lord has done.

00:02:16.796 --> 00:02:28.639
And I'm just so thankful that you would come on and watch with us every single time we do a video, stick around, watch it, and believe in the gifting that God's put inside of me.

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:33.677
It's just exciting. So that was part of it, you know, just saying thank you.

00:02:33.678 --> 00:02:37.480
Thank you. God bless every single one of you. Thank you for watching.

00:02:37.481 --> 00:02:42.755
So, I want to talk to you all about what I saw in our last prayer video.

00:02:42.756 --> 00:02:48.389
And I didn't go over this from the last one about the pews of fire.

00:02:48.390 --> 00:02:54.958
And folks, it's time to get excited. The glorious church without spot or wrinkle.

00:02:54.959 --> 00:03:06.184
I'm telling you, I saw wooden pews. And it was the same church the Lord showed me, and the bell towers.

00:03:06.185 --> 00:03:14.874
Remember He said, "I'm giving one last call."And I saw the bells beginning to ring, one last alarm, one last call again.

00:03:14.875 --> 00:03:22.405
He showed this to me over and over again, but I saw the same church this time, and I could see through the church.

00:03:22.406 --> 00:03:28.427
And as I was looking through this beautiful church, it was in an old country area again.

00:03:28.428 --> 00:03:36.639
It was like an old Pentecostal country church in a rural area.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:42.505
And I could see the podium there, and there was a man of fire behind it.

00:03:42.506 --> 00:03:49.129
Then I looked at the pews, and they were the old wooden pews made out of oak.

00:03:49.130 --> 00:03:55.199
And I could see individual fires that were sitting on the pews.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:04:02.802
They were these massive fireballs, but they were small for the kids and they were large for the adults.

00:04:02.803 --> 00:04:10.672
And as I looked into this church, the pews were full of fire, but each individual fire was there.

00:04:10.673 --> 00:04:16.149
And I was like, "Oh."And I wanted to stop and just look at it, but every single fire was a different color.

00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:29.456
There were blue fires and red fires and all kinds of really cool fires, but they were all focused at the big fire on the stage where the pastor was preaching, which caused fires in the pews.

00:04:29.457 --> 00:04:53.839
The Lord said, "I want you to see what's on the front porch."And I saw a field full of babies that were crying, and some of them had sailor outfits on—like those old baby sailor outfits with the anchor on them and the red bow tie, or a red thing around their neck.

00:04:53.840 --> 00:05:03.039
And they were all crying. And the Lord spoke to me and He said, "The babies are coming.

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:12.262
I want you to be very patient with My babies. For once, you were a baby and you needed patience.

00:05:12.263 --> 00:05:21.666
You needed to have extra care, for there are many babies that are about to come to the church."He said, "Brandon, don't be hasty with them.

00:05:21.667 --> 00:05:30.099
Don't be cranky. Be patient and walk in love towards them, for you were once a baby, too."And He warned me about the babies.

00:05:30.100 --> 00:05:33.518
He said, "The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:41.698
Just treat the babies that are coming with care, for there are a lot of babies."He said, "Disciple them.

00:05:41.699 --> 00:05:49.038
Disciple the babies, for there's going to be a lot of them. Don't be mean to them.

00:05:49.039 --> 00:06:03.499
Be patient."And I saw elderly women—which I know this was not all elderly women—but they had the old '50s clothes on, they had the old '50s hair.

00:06:03.500 --> 00:06:11.598
They looked like Leave It to Beaver moms. Wow. And they were taking care of the babies dressed up like little Leave It to Beavers.

00:06:11.599 --> 00:06:15.577
Now, I thought that was interesting because it was like an old '50s style in this vision.

00:06:15.577 --> 00:06:20.865
But I saw their hair was all that old '50s hair with the old '50s clothes.

00:06:20.866 --> 00:06:25.186
And they were loving on these babies outside, and they were like mothers.

00:06:25.187 --> 00:06:47.133
And the Lord showed me, "There'll be many mothers that are there to help love these new babies, for you'll have to be like a mother to them."And I saw spiritual mothers rising up, spiritual parents to help take care of these babies, because you need a Leave It to Beaver mama to nurture them, a nurturing mother.

00:06:47.134 --> 00:07:00.694
I thought it was interesting because that's the '50s mom, like Leave It to Beaver kind of people, or those old '50s shows.

00:07:00.695 --> 00:07:07.839
But it's just amazing because that's the way the Lord was painting this to me: we must take care of these babies and disciple them.

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:12.843
So that was part of the vision that I saw, and the storm going on outside.

00:07:12.844 --> 00:07:21.783
The babies were crying, and God said, "Bring them in and just love on them."And so, it really blessed me, and that's why I kept that out.

00:07:21.784 --> 00:07:45.983
The Holy Spirit—I told Braden, I said, "That needs to be at the front of the video, what the Lord was telling us about the babies that are coming, because it doesn't need to be buried."There are a lot of times there's so much there that the Lord is giving us that it's an hour-long video, and there are a lot of you who don't hear that part, but this was so important that we set this apart.

00:07:45.984 --> 00:07:57.982
Another part of the vision that I saw in the previous video, I saw massive boat anchor chains. They were huge, like you would see on a massive ship.

00:07:57.983 --> 00:08:08.414
They were thick, thick chains, and they were stretching clear into the soil of the earth in Tulsa, and they were going straight up into heaven.

00:08:08.415 --> 00:08:13.846
But there was no end to the chain; I couldn't see where it ended, and I couldn't see where it began.

00:08:13.847 --> 00:08:21.013
Both ends were pulled so tight in the vision, but there was a chain in Tulsa.

00:08:21.014 --> 00:08:28.079
I saw one in the Branson area, I saw one in the Kansas City area, and I saw one in Fort Worth.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:37.423
And these chains were pulled tight, and they were pulling the earth, but the chains were gold, like a transparent gold.

00:08:37.424 --> 00:08:46.662
This beautiful gold, like you've never seen before—maybe in a cartoon, but never in real life. This was the most beautiful gold.

00:08:46.663 --> 00:09:04.234
But the gold was sparkling with the glory and it was being pulled, and you could actually see the torque from the earth pulling up like when you're pulling something out of the earth, like tree roots or something.

00:09:04.235 --> 00:09:11.388
You could see the dirt being pulled up on the sides of this massive chain, and it was going straight into the heavens.

00:09:11.389 --> 00:09:18.793
And I could see the grass, and I could see the dirt, and all of the stress of the earth where it was being pulled.

00:09:18.794 --> 00:09:26.239
Now, I don't know what that means, but I believe it has something to do with the end-time glory. And there was a pull there.

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:40.498
And I kept hearing Jacob's ladder and portals of glory pulled tight, with no slack in the chain at all—portals of glory.

00:09:40.499 --> 00:09:55.963
And I'm telling you, when the Lord showed me again about the major revival that's about to take place in Branson, Missouri, Tulsa, and Fort Worth, Texas, and all these areas—those are just some of the areas that the Lord is showing me.

00:09:55.964 --> 00:10:05.470
It doesn't mean those are the only areas. I want to let you know there's going to be many places where the outpouring is going to be, but this is where the Lord showed me at this particular time.

00:10:05.471 --> 00:10:09.725
So, I just thought it was amazing what the Lord was showing me about this.

00:10:09.726 --> 00:10:16.913
So, now, after I go over all those things and I saw the glory—I saw the fall time again, I keep seeing the fall.

00:10:16.914 --> 00:10:23.939
There's something about the fall. It's time to rest it all. There's going to be an outpouring. There are things starting to kick off, folks.

00:10:23.940 --> 00:10:31.691
When we go into this Rosh Hashanah, this major holy day, a transfer, there's something happening.

00:10:31.692 --> 00:10:36.674
He started talking to me about being ankle deep, knee deep, waist deep, over the head.

00:10:36.675 --> 00:10:41.255
And I'm telling you, folks, what we're about to see, we're not even—we're just barely in the shadow.

00:10:41.256 --> 00:10:45.958
We're just at the shallows of it. We just slipped our feet in there. We're just kind of tiptoeing around.

00:10:45.959 --> 00:10:50.075
We got our toes in there, and we're like splashing around with our Holy Ghost toes.

00:10:50.076 --> 00:11:03.314
But what God's about to do, we're going to go clear to the bottom of the massive well that He has for us with no limitation.

00:11:03.315 --> 00:11:07.112
Yes. There's no limitation for what the Lord has in store for us.

00:11:07.113 --> 00:11:13.900
And I'm telling you, it's time to believe God like you've never believed Him before.

00:11:13.901 --> 00:11:19.567
For there's Holy Ghost fire in the pews, and I'm telling you all, it's all hands on deck.

00:11:19.568 --> 00:11:26.748
'All ye that are heavy laden, I will give you rest.'Who's hungry? Who's thirsty for the next outpouring?

00:11:26.749 --> 00:11:37.634
And I'm telling you, folks, He's just looking for a yielded one to say, 'Father, here am I, send me.'There's no one going to be any greater than—well, you know, He's branding this.

00:11:37.635 --> 00:11:43.411
I'm telling you, folks, it's not about platform. It's about yieldedness. It's about obedience.

00:11:43.412 --> 00:11:56.714
He said, 'Brandon, I'm looking for the people who think they have such big platforms.'He said, 'The reason why they've stayed there so long and they've not increased in the glory is because I look at the heart of obedience.

00:11:56.715 --> 00:12:06.479
I reward the obedient, just like you do when your child is obedient and they are good kids and they do what you tell them to do.

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:10.929
You say, "Pull out the trash, do these things,"and then they do things without you even asking.

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:13.270
You're like, "Oh, buddy, you're going to get blessed today.

00:12:13.271 --> 00:12:20.870
I want to take you to go get an ice cream or something fun."You know, you just want to reward your kids.'And God is a God of rewards.

00:12:20.871 --> 00:12:29.727
And He is going to abundantly supply in these last days, not just finances, but ladies and gentlemen, He's going to pour out His Spirit upon all flesh.

00:12:29.728 --> 00:12:36.879
And you're going to see some of the greatest things you've ever seen. It's going to be, you know, from what I've seen coming.

00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:41.390
And I keep saying that over and over, but I keep getting glimpses of it when I'm praying.

00:12:41.391 --> 00:12:48.243
And the Lord keeps telling me, 'Brandon, do you understand? It's more than just the finances. It's more.

00:12:48.244 --> 00:12:59.638
It's the whole man: spirit, soul, and body.'Just like Oral Roberts says, 'I'm here to minister to the whole man: spirit, soul, and body.'He wants us free in every area of our life.

00:12:59.639 --> 00:13:06.966
Not, 'Well, you know, you've got money, but you're depressed,'or, 'Well, you're whole, but you're broke.

00:13:06.967 --> 00:13:19.968
I don't have any sickness in my body, and I'm thankful for it, Lord, but you're broke.'He's like, 'I want to do over and above all that you dare ask or think according to the power that worketh in you.'What do you believe Me for?

00:13:19.969 --> 00:13:27.598
Will you believe Me for big today? Will you believe Me for the impossible? What was impossible will become possible.

00:13:27.599 --> 00:13:35.829
I'm going to take what you thought would be something that you'd be bound by your whole life, and it's going to be set-free time.

00:13:35.830 --> 00:13:46.394
I'm telling you, there's an expiration date to everything you're believing for. And it's time to believe God for big in these last days.

00:13:46.395 --> 00:13:52.632
Yes, I say a lot of heavy words, and I tell you a lot of warnings, and that's where I'm going next.

00:13:52.633 --> 00:14:01.378
But I wanted to give you something good to munch on while you're about to eat something a little sour because of what He showed me.

00:14:01.379 --> 00:14:05.919
But I just have to tell you, I tell you everything, and I'm just bold about it.

00:14:05.920 --> 00:14:10.040
But I'm not worried about it. I'm looking up, for my redemption draws nigh.

00:14:10.041 --> 00:14:15.023
But I want to tell you, there are hard times ahead for some folks because they're not looking.

00:14:15.024 --> 00:14:21.178
Now, let's go into praying over Don Jr., okay, and all that the Lord showed us.

00:14:21.179 --> 00:14:37.759
So, the Lord showed me the White House, and I could see demonic witchcraft all over Washington, D.C.—a heavy, thick witchcraft trying to settle in over the White House, over President Trump's health.

00:14:37.760 --> 00:14:57.564
We must pray for President Trump's health, for I saw an attack trying to give him a stroke because of all the pressure, all the demonic worry, and all the stress trying to affect his immune system, trying to affect him with so much stress that he would have a heart attack or a stroke.

00:14:57.565 --> 00:15:14.988
And the Lord said, 'Pray over his heart for the circulation of the blood flowing through his veins, for there's an attack against his veins.'And I saw his arteries in his neck and in his head trying to affect him, to take him out through demonic pressure.

00:15:14.989 --> 00:15:30.383
It's heavy, this Antichrist agenda. So I saw it all swirling above the White House, and it looked like the clouds in a portal turning like a hurricane above it.

00:15:30.384 --> 00:15:40.645
There were purples and blacks and dark colors that were circling like a hurricane above, and it was turning and turning all above.

00:15:40.646 --> 00:15:44.957
And I could see it; it stretched clear into the Atlantic Ocean.

00:15:44.957 --> 00:15:56.719
And I could see it over the Capitol; I could see it over where Congress, the judges, and all of it was. It was trying to come in over Washington, D.C.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:16:07.377
But inside of the White House were these lights, and there was light inside the home, and it looked like there was peace inside the house.

00:16:07.378 --> 00:16:15.278
As there was a storm brewing outside, there was light on the inside. And the Lord said, 'Focus on the light.

00:16:15.279 --> 00:16:19.198
Look at the light, son.'And I could see a light inside the White House.

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:24.479
There was a storm brewing on the outside, but there was light on the inside.

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:40.159
And the Lord said, 'Pray for him more.'Then I saw, Qasem Soleimani, I saw generals on oil-based paintings and frames that were really beautiful frames.

00:16:40.160 --> 00:16:50.488
But as—and I'll describe this as, if you remember the movie Back to the Future, as he was making the decision and he was singing on the stage and he was playing Johnny B.

00:16:50.489 --> 00:16:57.750
Goode and his brothers and sisters on the photo were fading away. Remember how they were fading away?

00:16:57.751 --> 00:17:03.650
If you've watched the movie—I know it's an old movie—but it was fading away. And this is the way these photos looked.

00:17:03.651 --> 00:17:13.198
I could see these Iranian generals and they were fading away, and below this picture was fire, and it was consuming.

00:17:13.199 --> 00:17:20.194
And I said, "They're in hell,"and I could see the fire burning these men, for they looked like spirits.

00:17:20.195 --> 00:17:28.719
They looked like ghosts, and as the fire was burning the pictures, they said, "We want revenge.

00:17:28.720 --> 00:17:35.149
We want revenge."And I saw their generals in a line in the photos, and they were burning.

00:17:35.150 --> 00:17:39.275
And in the photos, these people were fading away, and they were burning in hell.

00:17:39.276 --> 00:17:48.959
And the Lord showed me Don Jr., and he became a photo, and the fire was trying to eat him.

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:57.322
And the Lord said, "You must intercede for Don Jr., for there's an attempt coming on his life."I want to say this again.

00:17:57.323 --> 00:18:02.807
You must intercede for Don Jr., for there is an attempt coming on his life.

00:18:02.808 --> 00:18:19.145
For they say, "If we cannot get to Trump, we will take out his son in revenge of what he did to our generals."So I saw a plan and a plot to shoot and assassinate Don Jr.

00:18:19.146 --> 00:18:28.605
to take him out. I saw him in a tuxedo with a white shirt with black stud buttons.

00:18:28.606 --> 00:18:37.865
It was a cover, like one of those pleated-looking shirts, nice ones, a tuxedo-looking shirt, and he was dressed up for something nice.

00:18:37.866 --> 00:18:45.749
I saw President Kennedy, and the Lord said, "The Kennedy curse."I saw the Cuban missile crisis.

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:56.558
God said, "Pay attention to Cuba."And I could see Cuba again, and I could see missiles, and I could see things pointed at the United States of America.

00:18:56.559 --> 00:19:09.568
And the Lord showed me Kennedy with Donald Trump and what's going to happen, a plan with the kids. But I want to tell you this ahead of time.

00:19:09.569 --> 00:19:18.976
The Lord said to say this before, "What will you do as watchmen on this channel to intercede in behalf of Trump's children?

00:19:18.977 --> 00:19:25.556
What will we do to stop these plans, for this is an attempt? You must stop the plans.

00:19:25.557 --> 00:19:33.001
You must bring this before the people in prayer and cover his family in prayer. Cover his heart, for this is not God's will.

00:19:33.002 --> 00:19:44.193
This is an enemy attack."And the Lord said, "After you've seen all this, what are you going to do about it?

00:19:44.194 --> 00:19:49.632
What are you going to do about this?"I thought, "Well, we'll raise up a standard.

00:19:49.633 --> 00:19:54.319
We'll pray."When the enemy tries to come in, the Spirit of the Lord raises a standard against him.

00:19:54.320 --> 00:20:04.459
I believe that's why we're here, ladies and gentlemen, is to pray these things down. So, I saw Don Jr. walking out.

00:20:04.460 --> 00:20:13.792
I don't know where it was, but I saw flashing lights like photography, like the paparazzi, wherever he was. I could see the flashes of light on his face.

00:20:13.793 --> 00:20:46.246
It was like people were taking pictures of him, and all of a sudden, I saw these other people—like he was surrounded by other people in this event—and all of a sudden, he was shot right here in his chest, and I saw a bloodstain on that white shirt start to spread like a half-dollar size, and I kept hearing the word "AK-47."I kept hearing a loud noise, and he was gone.

00:20:46.247 --> 00:21:01.195
It was one shot. Then I went to President Trump, and I could see him weeping because of what had happened, and he was in so much stress and travail.

00:21:01.196 --> 00:21:12.719
He was bent over, travailing, weeping because of his son being taken out, so upset, like anybody would be if their child was murdered.

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:27.994
I saw him travailing and crying. When I start seeing that vision again, I could see the funeral, and he could barely walk.

00:21:27.995 --> 00:21:39.556
He was grieving so bad. He could barely walk; he was stumbling, and they had to help hold him up as he was weeping over his son's life being taken.

00:21:39.557 --> 00:21:54.283
I could see Barron. He was wearing a black suit with a white shirt and a black tie, similar to what he wore on the inauguration. And then I could see Melania, and she had a black hat on.

00:21:54.284 --> 00:22:18.837
She had a black veil on her face that you could see through, like a net, but it was very classy-looking, and it was over her face, and she had black sunglasses on and a black dress on, and it had a little white on its side, and she was trying to support Trump as he was walking to the funeral.

00:22:18.838 --> 00:22:24.842
And I could see the other children there, but it was mainly those three in the vision that were very clear.

00:22:24.843 --> 00:22:30.535
Ivanka was there. I could see Ivanka, and she was crying, too, and she had a hat on.

00:22:30.536 --> 00:22:37.058
But the church looked like the church where they went before the inauguration.

00:22:37.059 --> 00:22:43.754
It looked like that church they went to for prayer, like at the cathedral.

00:22:43.755 --> 00:22:48.168
It looked like that exact place. That's where they were having this funeral.

00:22:48.169 --> 00:22:54.586
And that's when the Lord said, "What are you going to do about it? What are you going to do to stop it? Are you going to pray?

00:22:54.587 --> 00:23:01.733
Are you going to intercede for this man?"So that's what I bring to you, these things that are very heavy.

00:23:01.734 --> 00:23:12.438
Now, part two of this vision, I saw New York City on fire. I saw fires all throughout New York City.

00:23:12.439 --> 00:23:20.498
I could see the Statue of Liberty, and there was smoke rolling all around the atmosphere above the Statue of Liberty.

00:23:20.499 --> 00:23:28.731
Even at her neck level, there was fire and smoke from inside the city, and I could see burning.

00:23:28.732 --> 00:23:38.042
But I saw a mass exodus of all the rich people leaving New York because of the decisions that will be made in the future.

00:23:38.043 --> 00:24:04.079
I saw—the Lord said, "The seed is the ballot, for when they vote a wrong person in power, they vote corruption in power, and the seeds they sow for the corruption, Brandon, brings forth a reprobate mind in the city, a reprobate mind in the city, for seedtime and harvest never ceases.

00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:08.891
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap."He said, "There's a time to live, and there's a time to die.

00:24:08.892 --> 00:24:18.035
There's a time to sow, and there's a time to reap, a time to plant, and a time to harvest."But he kept going over things and telling me this is because they sow this way.

00:24:18.036 --> 00:24:24.478
So I saw all the rich people leaving. I saw a mass—hundreds of thousands of people were leaving New York City in this vision.

00:24:24.479 --> 00:24:32.252
And the Lord showed me David Wilkerson's face, and he said, "Remember what he said.

00:24:32.253 --> 00:24:37.460
